10
00:01:05,318 --> 00:01:07,547
Hello, my name is Jeon Jin Ho.

11
00:01:07,547 --> 00:01:09,880
Hello, I am Park Kae In.

12
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:11,866
I hope you treat me well.

13
00:01:11,866 --> 00:01:13,246
