34
00:02:32,462 --> 00:02:34,373
Aigoo, I don't know.

35
00:02:43,938 --> 00:02:46,041
Jeon Jin Ho,

36
00:02:46,041 --> 00:02:48,679
you have become braver!

37
00:02:57,353 --> 00:03:02,333
