98
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:35,696
Jeon Jin Ho's forehead.

99
00:07:37,359 --> 00:07:39,980
Jeon Jin Ho's nose.

100
00:07:40,603 --> 00:07:43,362
Jeon Jin Ho's lips.

101
00:07:51,714 --> 00:07:54,556
